CustomerService -> CustomerDB: Query Invoice + InvoiceItem by customer
CustomerDB --> CustomerService: Invoice rows with items
CustomerService --> Gateway: Invoice list payload
Gateway --> Customer: Render invoice list

Customer -> Gateway: GET /api/customers/invoices/{invoice_id}/
Gateway -> CustomerService: GET /customers/invoices/{invoice_id}/
